      <title>由于贷款回撤影响信用卡收入，NerdWallet 下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/nerdwallet-falls-as-lending-pullback-hurts-credit-card-revenue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[NerdWallet Inc.因发行人收紧贷款而导致其主要信用卡收入下降，尽管国际扩张和新的投资发行预计将有助于今年晚些时候恢复增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/nerdwallet-falls-as-lending-pullback-hurts-credit-card-revenue</guid>
